# Required for the functional tier (test/functional/) and the real-Pythonx
# integration tier (any test exercising GraphitiPool's shared LLM/embedder/
# cross_encoder construction or graphiti operations like search/add_episode).
#
# Without this credential, those tests surface graphiti's auth error
# unwrapped — there is no pre-flight gate.
#
# Get a key at https://aistudio.google.com/apikey, then copy this file
# to .env (gitignored) and fill it in.
GOOGLE_API_KEY=
